Text: GreetingsJeff Ive landed at Porter Novelli Im very happy its a good move for me Reading about Enron in Tuesdays UTgeez Ill be traveling to SF quite frequently in the next couple of monthsthink we can pull our schedules together to grab dinner one night Id love to catch upbut if you get to SD Jesse Knight is in the same building Kill two birds with one stone Dana Dana Perino Porter Novelli Convergence Group
